DISCLAIMER — MEDICAL CONTENT

The medical rules bundled in this repository (under ``rules/``) are for
software-flow validation only; they are NOT a clinical decision support
system and MUST NOT be used to make medical decisions. The synthetic
recall-pressure fixtures (1000 / 10000 patient_state decoys) are
stress-test fixtures, NOT real medical rules. Always consult a licensed
physician or pharmacist for any medical advice.